                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17991030-34-off193 t17991030-34-cd194"></join>, a waggon tilt cloth, value 3l. 3s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17991030-34-victim347" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Bellis
                  <interp inst="t17991030-34-victim347" type="surname" value="Bellis"></interp>
