                     <interp inst="t17991030-34-person349" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - I am a labourer; I was with 
               <persName id="t17991030-34-person350">
                  Joseph
                   Ward
               <interp inst="t17991030-34-person350" type="surname" value="Ward"></interp>
